### 评论功能 API 测试文件
### 基础 URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7005
@blogId = 7880BCD9-A178-423C-B8A6-F1912C1BDFEA
@userId = 5154DC2C-782D-4872-89DA-A78030EF7BD6
@commentId = 7a178f3d-0a3c-42b3-8f63-0c3f2556e5f1

### 1. 创建顶级评论（不带 parentCommentId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blogId": "{{blogId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "content": "这是一条测试评论！"
}

### 1.1 创建顶级评论（带 null 的 parentCommentId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blogId": "{{blogId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "content": "这是另一条测试评论！",
  "parentCommentId": null
}

### 2. 创建回复评论
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blogId": "{{blogId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "content": "这是对评论的回复！",
  "parentCommentId": "{{commentId}}"
}

### 3. 获取博客的所有评论（包含回复树）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/blog/{{blogId}}

### 4. 获取单个评论详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/{{commentId}}

### 5. 更新评论内容
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/{{commentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "content": "这是更新后的评论内容"
}

### 6. 点赞评论
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/{{commentId}}/like
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isLiked": true
}

### 7. 取消点赞评论
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/{{commentId}}/like
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isLiked": false
}

### 8. 获取用户的所有评论
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/user/{{userId}}

### 9. 删除评论
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Comment/{{commentId}}
